  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Inclusive education for disabled children in Binga</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This is the package for donors funding a project to provide inclusive education for disable children in Binga, Zimbabwe. This is a 2 year project which will directly benefit 1,020 children living with disabilities, as well as their families (approx. 445), from 5 wards in Binga district. There are multiple donors for this project, including the Porticus Foundation, the Women&apos;s World Day of Prayer and the Isle of Man Supporter Committee.</narrative>
  </description>
